RUN 'GO VAR' TO INSTALL NEWAMPERSAND   FUNCTIONALITY.USE '& GOTO expr' AND '& GOSUB expr'TO JUMP TO A LINE NUMBER DEFINED BYAN     EXPRESSION.ALSO; '& RETURN' IS A VERSION OF THE'RETURN' COMMAND WITH AN OBSCURE BUGFIXED.  IN THE NORMAL APPLESOFTVERSION;A 'RETURN WITHOUT GOSUB'ERRORINCORRECTLY APPEARS IF A FOR LOOP ISACTIVE WHEN THE 'RETURN' COMMAND ISGIVEN; AND IF THE FOR LOOP VARIABLEIS  STORED AT A LOCATION $xxFF.